Author: FeatherMahogany59
Text: I feel this really hard. I have very very disordered thoughts but my restriction usually still hits close to 1,000 calories. And I am totally average weight. It’s so embarrassing that my fat ass has an eating disorder. I just fail at everything. Like, I can’t even have a mental illness correctly. 😂😂😂   your struggle is valid ❤️ you deserve to feel good about yourself
